data.description:
Newly remodeled 4 bedroom 1.5 bath home in Provo. Granite countertops and large kitchen & dining area with spacious family and living rooms. Space for multiple vehicles with a covered carport for 2 vehicles.

*6 month lease agreement

Amenities: Air Conditioning, Basement (Finished), Covered Parking/Car Port, Dishwasher, Disposal, Family Room, Fenced Yard (Part), Granite Countertops, Living Room, Microwave, Near BYU, Near UVU, Newly Remodeled, Refrigerator, Shed, Sprinklers Auto, Stove/Oven, Washer/Dryer Hookups
